 term. We also apply our path integral techniques to give\na compact derivation of the semiclassical approximation to the coherent state\npropagator.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Jul 2008 13:43:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 30 Jul 2008 16:53:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-05-29"}
